{"tid":959211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大學生陳展楠發起聯署 希望麥當勞停止派發飲品膠袋","createTime":"2018-12-28T11:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T12:08:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b98c1dc1c7ba8eb13b8068feb838de309f31818c","tid":959211,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20170304/19946462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170304%2F19946462&d=Ao%2FHfrXoLeIqV7piS8XTtsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ee273df4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170304%2F19946462&h=7811b0f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20170304/19946462</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170304/large/04fe401p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170304%2Flarge%2F04fe401p.jpg&h=fcc9e4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阮庭蔚（左）及陳展楠在網上發起聯署，希望麥當勞停止向顧客派發飲品膠袋。<br />\n<br />\n香港人習慣高速解決三餐，快餐成為很多人的心水，不知不覺造成垃圾問題。其中麥當勞盛載外賣飲品的聚乙烯膠袋派派派，令堆填區內不能分解的膠製品與日俱增，有城市大學學生睇唔過眼，年初發起網上聯署，希望麥當勞「走膠袋」，他們強調消費者亦有責任，向多餘的膠袋說不。<br />\n<br />\n「唔使袋啦，唔該。」城大英文系四年級生陳展楠（Darian）友善地向又一城麥當勞收銀員表達飲品走袋的意願。由於每間店舖分工細緻，收銀、預備食物及執餐的店員都不同，Darian領餐時又見到兩杯可樂都分別入了袋，他都不厭其煩重複訊息。「好多人知道膠袋唔環保，同客人傾開，佢哋先意識到攞咗袋。」他和五位同學最近都留意港人耗膠的報道，根據環保署數字，2015年有2,183公噸膠丟到堆填區。身為M記外賣粉絲的阮庭蔚（Kristy）十分驚訝，覺得係時候做啲嘢，今年一月底發起網上聯署，希望M記停止向顧客派發盛載外賣飲品的膠袋，至今已收到500多個簽名。<br />\n<br />\n以麥當勞做目標，皆因它是本港快餐店龍頭大哥，Darian指，「其他快餐店把所有東西放在同一個袋，但麥當勞每個飲品都畀袋。」在麥當勞官網寫明，為了推動環保，他們承諾客人如購買單杯非密封飲品，不會主動提供膠袋，Kristy慨嘆事實並非如此，「我哋用了個多月，去全港15間分店，觀察客人用膠袋的情況，有啲誇張到堂食都畀袋，係咪太嚴重呢？」有人覺得，汽水唔畀袋，拎住會整濕隻手，擺喺枱又整濕，好麻煩。Kristy建議可使用循環再造的紙杯代替膠袋。"},{"pid":"e90de98c37d808ff27ed3a2afa9c7df13bb3a66d","tid":959211,"uid":202170,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNKk0Ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNKk0Ue.png&h=604d1a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bd3ba3192da764149dd322c2032ff6ffd96c69","tid":959211,"uid":123308,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"唔係影張相，攞光環，想第時見工畀相人睇話係環保鬥士吓話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62f5bd42d8a8105147f496bb878480c92f661ea","tid":959211,"uid":173239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"條女more<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f27ba70f59f11e62a536012d745bbaac4a1bc32","tid":959211,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8bd3ba3192da764149dd322c2032ff6ffd96c69","tid":959211,"uid":123308,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"唔係影張相，攞光環，想第時見工畀相人睇話係環保鬥士吓話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"入硬NGO，叻仔"},{"pid":"0e2e0d90dd8062d06443ba182847330803a6c17b","tid":959211,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死肥仔"},{"pid":"994eb6e2f382c687a587075fd26abd6f90ea7c83","tid":959211,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e90de98c37d808ff27ed3a2afa9c7df13bb3a66d","tid":959211,"uid":202170,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"repl